;
Punta del Morro , Veracruz , Mexico ( Britton & Morton 1989 ); Lobos Reef ,
100 km SSE Tampico
, Mexico ( USNM 710352 )
;
Key West , Florida ( USNM 435308 )
;
Cape Canaveral Inlet , Florida ( USNM 820427 )
;
